<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<mvt:item name="html_profile" />
<head>
	<mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if>
	<mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" />
	<mvt:comment>
		Category Hub V2 staging template. Inactive only. Do not assign over live CTGY.
		Updated to match live ctgy.mvt behavior: always delegate subcategory-vs-product
		decisioning to the native <mvt:item name="category_listing" /> module (same as
		Merchandise & Apparel and every other live category page), instead of a custom
		subcategory_count/category_depth tile-grid gate. That custom gate incorrectly
		forced a subcategory tile grid (or an empty placeholder) on leaf categories that
		should show products.
	</mvt:comment>
</head>
<body>
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />

<main class="sd2-v2-search-page" data-v2-category-hub>
	<div class="sd2-wrap">
		<header class="sd2-v2-search-page__head">
			<nav class="sd2-v2-breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
				<a href="&mvte:urls:SFNTV2:auto;">Home</a>
				<span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
				<span>&mvte:category:name;</span>
			</nav>
			<div class="sd2-v2-search-page__title-row">
				<div>
					<p class="sd2-eyebrow">Product Listing</p>
					<h1 class="sd2-heading-lg">&mvte:category:name;</h1>
				</div>
				<p class="sd2-v2-search-page__count">&mvte:category_listing:total_prod_count; products</p>
			</div>
			<mvt:if expr="l.settings:category:descrip">
				<div class="sd2-body">&mvt:category:descrip;</div>
			<mvt:else>
				<p class="sd2-body">[Placeholder] Category introduction renders from Miva category description when available.</p>
			</mvt:if>
		</header>
	</div>

	<div class="sd2-wrap">
		<mvt:comment>TODO: register Vehicle Banner V2 in Miva Admin as readytheme contentsection('vehicle_banner') before using mvt:item composition.</mvt:comment>
	</div>

	<div class="sd2-wrap">
		<mvt:if expr="l.settings:facets:facet_count GT 0">
			<mvt:assign name="l.settings:sd2_ctgy_layout_class" value="'sd2-v2-search-page__layout sd2-v2-search-page__layout--has-filters'" />
		<mvt:else>
			<mvt:assign name="l.settings:sd2_ctgy_layout_class" value="'sd2-v2-search-page__layout sd2-v2-search-page__layout--no-filters'" />
		</mvt:if>
		<section class="&mvte:sd2_ctgy_layout_class;" aria-label="Category products">
			<aside class="sd2-v2-filter-rail" aria-label="Filters">
				<mvt:item name="facets" />
			</aside>

			<mvt:item name="category_listing" />
		</section>
	</div>
</main>

	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="footer" />
	<mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_footer" />
</body>
</html>
